Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:47.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ただ刷り込まれたビジョン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無限遠点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}価値観を今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}上書きする　変哲の無い宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:04.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傲慢な神は目に映らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:09.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光速度で支配続けるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:14.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕は　僕だけは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}奇跡的で致命的な
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}マイノリティでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I can fly──
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あの瞬間、あの場面が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミにとって特別なら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:33.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}過去は離れて行くものなんかじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傷つく事の痛みより
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}大事なシーン　その全ての
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:44.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ヒカリが今ゼロを生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wonderful new world.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------OPCN---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果当今的天地并非现实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:47.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仅仅只是一个虚妄的掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无限远方那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:55.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}价值观逐渐畸变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}逐步重建 不起涟漪宇宙间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:04.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}各路诸神心傲慢 藐视万物的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:09.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仍以为光速 还能支配到宇宙天边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:14.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}对是我 只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}是极其罕见的致命异类之种
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即将燎遍禁锢的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自由翱翔──
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:25.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那个瞬间 还是那些画面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:28.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那些留恋 留在你的心间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:33.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去的那些琐事决未从此消失 也未曾远逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去那些伤痛 再也不要提及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}回忆那些留恋 是你成长阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:44.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}用回忆的光将零之门 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}从此再无神明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}欢迎美丽新世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------EDJP---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:16.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Embrace my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:22.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Let me guide you down into my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:28.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}And let us pray for the world to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:35.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The truth within us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Emptiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:41.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Erodes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:47.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Cuz you're free from pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:54.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Future is just too bright to show you ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:56.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wake up now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:00.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}It's time to lead new souls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Orbit of photon and universe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:13.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I am just the part of its plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:20.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}目には見えない歪んだ空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:28.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人は何処へと歩いていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:32.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The last game
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------EDCN---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:16.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}拥抱我的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:22.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让我指引你到我的灵魂深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:28.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让我们为世界的苏醒而祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}这里和平而安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:35.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真理与我们共存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无尽的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:41.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}侵蚀你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:47.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}因为你从未遭受痛苦与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.42,0:22:54.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}未来太过刺眼 前路无法看清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:56.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}现在醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:00.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}指引新的灵魂的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:07.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光子与宇宙的运转轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:13.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我只是其中微不足道的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:20.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}双眼看不到的扭曲天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.82,0:23:28.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:32.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}最后的一场游戏
